// LeanSignal agent control-plane protocol, v1.
//
// The agent (in a private network) dials out to lean-api and opens ONE long-lived
// bidirectional stream (AgentControl.Connect). Both directions carry a oneof
// envelope; the server can push commands to the agent over the open stream, so no
// inbound connectivity to the agent is required. Authentication is via the
// "x-agent-key" gRPC metadata header on stream open.
